data.description: USDA ELIGIBLE AREA means possibility of ZERO DOWN PAYMENT! Property listed on a Value Range, Seller will consider offers between $369,000 - $399,000. Welcome to your dream home! Private and spacious brick home - with a POOL POOL POOL - on over 1.3 acres of fenced property, custom features throughout complete with a well laid out split bedroom floorplan. This 3 bedrooms - including a master en suite and 2 full bathroom home was designed for comfort and entertaining, with a brand new den or versatile space for a home office, game room, or whatever your heart desires! Gorgeous, large, open-concept kitchen with top-of-the-line LG stainless steel appliances, beautiful granite counter tops, custom cabinets, large pantry, and ample storage has plenty of seating available for guests and family. Separate formal dining room for private dinners or holiday entertaining complete with accentuating chandelier and tray ceilings. Recessed lighting throughout, along with ceiling fans for energy efficiency. Seamless flow from the front entry way all the way through the home to the rear custom designed covered patio and inground Gunite pool that's less than 2years old. Your personal oasis awaits! Modern upgrades and finishes throughout. WIRED REAR WORKSHOP in back of property, plenty of room for all your TOOLS, with 2 covered additions. Custom stamped concrete driveway and carport parking for side-entry of home; plenty of parking for everyone's needs. Buyer to verify accuracy of all measurements and details deemed pertinent to sale, listing brokerage makes no claim as to the accuracy of information provided. Cross listed in Baldwin Paragon MLS #35952
